<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 12:24:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>尼泊尔总理达哈尔失去议会信任票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepal-pm-dahal-loses-parliamentary-vote-confidence-2024-07-12/</link><description>尼泊尔总理普什帕·卡迈勒·达哈尔周五在议会信任投票中落败，结束了他长达 20 个月的混乱任期，他在四次信任投票中幸存下来，并为组建新的联合政府铺平了道路。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 11:48:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepal-pm-dahal-loses-parliamentary-vote-confidence-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>早间买盘：通货紧缩、轮动和美元受损</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-07-12/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 10:10:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>报道称，意大利将向中国汽车制造商提供已停产的 Stellantis 品牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-offer-defunct-stellantis-brands-chinese-automakers-report-says-2024-07-12/</link><description>据《Il Sole 24 Ore》周五报道，意大利政府正在考虑通过法令接管 Stellantis 旗下已不复存在的汽车品牌，并将其提供给中国企业，以鼓励它们在意大利设厂。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 09:53:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-offer-defunct-stellantis-brands-chinese-automakers-report-says-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国6月新增银行贷款未达预期，部分货币指标创历史新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-june-new-bank-loans-miss-forecasts-some-money-gauges-hit-record-lows-2024-07-12/</link><description>6月份，中国银行贷款增幅低于预期，而一些关键货币指标创下历史新低，突显出在中国最高领导人准备开会制定长期政策目标之际，世界第二大经济体的需求疲软。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 09:50:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-june-new-bank-loans-miss-forecasts-some-money-gauges-hit-record-lows-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国6月对俄罗斯出口增速较上月加快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-june-exports-russia-rise-more-quickly-than-previous-month-2024-07-12/</link><description>海关周五数据显示，6月份中国对俄罗斯以人民币计价的出口同比增长4.76%，高于5月份0.92%的增速，但仍远低于年初两位数的出口增速。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 07:07:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-june-exports-russia-rise-more-quickly-than-previous-month-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>台湾将从中正纪念堂撤走仪仗队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-withdraw-honour-guards-chiang-kai-shek-memorial-2024-07-12/</link><description>文化部周五表示，台湾将撤回前领导人蒋介石纪念馆的军事仪仗队，作为结束“对独裁主义崇拜”持续努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 06:37:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-withdraw-honour-guards-chiang-kai-shek-memorial-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国银行周一维持中期贷款利率不变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cbank-seen-holding-medium-term-lending-rate-steady-monday-2024-07-12/</link><description>路透调查显示，人们普遍预计中国央行周一将到期贷款展期时将维持中期利率不变，并从银行体系中抽走部分现金。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 06:01:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cbank-seen-holding-medium-term-lending-rate-steady-monday-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>瓦努阿图总理要求中国银行在维拉港开设分行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vanuatu-prime-minister-asks-bank-china-open-branch-port-villa-2024-07-12/</link><description>瓦努阿图总理夏洛特·萨尔瓦伊办公室周五在一份声明中表示，已要求中国银行在这个太平洋岛国开展业务。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 04:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vanuatu-prime-minister-asks-bank-china-open-branch-port-villa-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>即时观点：中国6月原油、未锻轧铜进口量同比下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-chinas-june-imports-drop-prospect-seasonal-demand-slowdown-2024-07-12/</link><description>周五海关数据显示，中国6月份大豆、煤炭和铁矿石进口量同比增加，而原油、未锻轧铜和稀土进口量下降。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 04:09:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-chinas-june-imports-drop-prospect-seasonal-demand-slowdown-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国出口高于预期，但进口下降意味着更多刺激措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-rise-falling-imports-dampen-june-trade-data-2024-07-12/</link><description>6月份，中国出口增速创15个月以来最快，这表明制造商在越来越多的贸易伙伴预期加征关税之前提前加载订单，而由于国内需求疲软，进口意外萎缩。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 03:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-exports-rise-falling-imports-dampen-june-trade-data-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责欧盟关于南海的声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-scolds-eu-over-statement-about-south-china-sea-2024-07-12/</link><description>中国谴责欧盟就南海问题发表的声明，称欧盟无视该问题的历史和客观事实，并“公然”支持其所谓的菲律宾侵犯其主权的行为。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 02:09:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-scolds-eu-over-statement-about-south-china-sea-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾拒绝“使用武力”损害其南海利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-rejects-any-undermining-its-south-china-sea-interests-2024-07-12/</link><description>官员周五表示，菲律宾拒绝“使用武力”损害其在有争议的南中国海的利益，但不希望发生任何冲突，并已与中国就缓解有争议的浅滩的紧张局势达成一致。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:44:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-rejects-any-undermining-its-south-china-sea-interests-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>股市将焦点转向盈利，外汇市场关注日本干预</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-12/</link><description>乐观的财报和美国降息的希望提振了周五股市的情绪，尽管在东京据信介入支撑疲弱日元的第二天，外汇市场上普遍存在不安情绪。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>商务部长表示中国愿意加强与沙特的贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-strengthen-trade-with-saudi-commerce-minister-says-2024-07-12/</link><description>中国商务部长周五在一份声明中表示，中国愿与沙特加强实施发展战略，密切贸易和投资交流。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:33:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-strengthen-trade-with-saudi-commerce-minister-says-2024-07-12/</guid></item><item><title>日本因不当处理机密信息而对军方高层进行纪律处分</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-pm-promises-discipline-military-mishandling-classified-information-2024-07-12/</link><description>日本周五对 200 多名国防人员进行了纪律处分，其中包括军方高级官员和高级官僚，原因是他们处理机密材料和其他事件不当。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 01:33:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-pm-promises-discipline-military-mishandling-classified-information-2024-07-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>